name: Frankenstyle.css
tagline: A collection of mixins, techniques, modules and style snippets taken from a number of front end frameworks. Feel free to use this, but know that I've built it for me so if you don't like something it's your fault, not mine :)
body:
Frankenstyle.css
================

A collection of mixins, techniques, modules and style snippets taken from a number of front end frameworks. Feel free to use this, but know that I've built it for me so if you don't like something it's your fault, not mine :)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
